# Loiter Test Mission
# Description: Tests different loiter modes and behaviors
#
# Mission Profile:
# - Takeoff to 100m
# - Navigate to first waypoint
# - Loiter 3 turns at 50m radius (NAV_LOITER_TURNS)
# - Navigate to second waypoint at 120m
# - Loiter for 30 seconds (NAV_LOITER_TIME)
# - Return and land
#
# Expected Duration: ~8 minutes
#
# Usage:
#   wp load loiter_test.waypoints
#   mode AUTO
#
# Good for:
# - Testing loiter radius accuracy
# - Bank angle limits
# - Wind compensation in circles
# - Timing accuracy
#
# Watch parameters:
# - WP_LOITER_RAD (loiter radius)
# - LIM_ROLL_CD (max roll angle)
# - NAVL1_PERIOD (L1 controller responsiveness)
#
# Author: Patrick Kelly (@Kuscko)
# Version: 1.0
